		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Re: Make link to wiki more prominent?</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />At some point in the past, people were considering having it be a redirect to <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/Nesdev">http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/Nesdev</a><!-- m --> so that we could maintain it.<br /><br />There's also something to be said for moving the images in, since it's a little goofy that we've got both <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/File:Neswires.jpg">http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/File:Neswires.jpg</a><!-- m --> and <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://nesdev.com/Ntd_8bit.jpg">http://nesdev.com/Ntd_8bit.jpg</a><!-- m --> now

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


